Package com.project.searching

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdjCostComparator
    Compares the price between two list items and returns the lowest of the two StationSearchResults list items.
    DistanceComparator
    Compares the distance from the users location to two stations, and return the closest station.
    FuelPrice
    Stores the value and the last update date of a fuel price.
    GasStation
    Stores the data associated with a gas station.
    GetJsonTask
    Subclass of AsyncTask which can be used to execute a HTTP request in the background.
    PriceComparator
    Compares the price between two list items and returns the lowest of the two StationSearchResults list items.
    StationAddress
    Stores the street address parts of a gas station.
    StationRequest
    Provides helper methods for performing a gas station search and for looking up a station by its myGasFeed station ID.
    StationSearchResult
    StationSearchResult lists the Results of the Gas Stations located within a 5 mile radius of the location.
    XMLAsyncDownloader
    Handles background downloading of vehicle information allowing SmartPump to continue running during the request.
    XMLParser
    Handles four types of parsing based on passed parseType value from 0 to 4.
